<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, user-scalable=no" />
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no, address=no, email=no" />
    <meta name="format-detection" content="no" />

    <title>다이어트 Farm 로그인</title>
    <%-include('general/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/signup.css">
</head>

<body>
    <section class="detail_title">
        <h2>회원가입</h2>
        <div class="btnback"><a href="#" value="취소" onclick="goBack()"><img src="/images/leftarrow_ico_my.png" alt=""> </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- wrapper -->
    <div id="wrapper">

        <!-- content-->
        <div id="content">
            <div class="signup_top">
                <!-- ID -->
                <div>
                    <h3 class="join_title">
                        <label for="id"><img src="/images/asterisk.png" style="width:2%">아이디</label>
                    </h3>
                    <span class="box int_id">
                        <input type="text" id="id" class="int" maxlength="20" placeholder="아이디" required>
                    </span>
                    <button type="button" onclick="id_check()">아이디 중복 확인</button>
                    <span class="error_next_box"></span>
                    <br>- 아이디 중복확인
                </div>

                <!-- PW1 -->
                <div>
                    <h3 class="join_title"><label for="pswd1"><img src="/images/asterisk.png" style="width:2%">비밀번호</label></h3>
                    <span class="box int_pass">
                        <input type="password" id="pswd1" class="int" maxlength="20" placeholder="비밀번호" required>
                        <span id="alertTxt">사용불가</span>
                        <img src="/images/m_icon_pass.png" id="pswd1_img1" class="pswdImg">
                    </span>
                    <span class="error_next_box"></span>
                    <p>- 10자 이상 입력</p>
                    <p>- 영문/숫자/특수문자 2개 이상 조합</p>
                </div>

                <!-- PW2 -->
                <div>
                    <h3 class="join_title"><label for="pswd2"><img src="/images/asterisk.png" style="width:2%">비밀번호 확인</label></h3>
                    <span class="box int_pass_check">
                        <input type="password" id="pswd2" class="int" maxlength="20" placeholder="비밀번호 재확인" required>
                        <img src="/images/m_icon_check_disable.png" id="pswd2_img1" class="pswdImg">
                    </span>
                    <span class="error_next_box"></span>
                </div>

                <!-- NAME -->
                <div>
                    <h3 class="join_title"><label for="name"><img src="/images/asterisk.png" style="width:2%">이메일</label></h3>
                    <span class="box int_name">
                        <input type="text" id="name" class="int" maxlength="20" required>
                    </span>
                    <span class="/images/error_next_box"></span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="join_title"><label for="addr"><img src="/images/asterisk.png" style="width:2%">주소</label></h3>
                    <span class="box int_addr">
                        <input type="text" id="addr" class="int" maxlength="80">
                    </span>
                    <span class="/images/error_next_box"></span>
                </div>

                <div style="padding-bottom:34px">
                    <h3 class="join_title"><label for="r_id">추천인 아이디</label></h3>
                    <span class="box int_r_id">
                        <input type="text" id="email" class="int" maxlength="100" placeholder="선택입력">
                    </span>
                    <span class="error_next_box">이메일 주소를 다시 확인해주세요.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="terms">
                <p><img src="/images/asterisk.png" style="width:2%"><span>이용약관동의</span></p>
                <p><input type="checkbox"><span>전체 동의합니다.</span></p>
                <p class="gray">선택 항목에 동의하지 않은 경우도 회원가입 및 일반적인 서비스를 이용할 수 있습니다.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><input type="checkbox" required>이용약관 <span>(필수)</span><a href="#"><img class="leftarrow" src="./images/arrow_ico_join.png" alt="화살표" style="width:2.2%"></a></li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox" required> 개인정보처리방침 <span>(필수)</span><a href="#"><img class="leftarrow" src="./images/arrow_ico_join.png" alt="화살표" style="width:2.2%"></a></li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox" required>본인은 만 14세 이상입니다. <span>(필수)</span><a href="#"><img class="leftarrow" src="./images/arrow_ico_join.png" alt="화살표" style="width:2.2%"></a></li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox">마케팅 수신동의 <span>(선택)</span><input type="checkbox">이메일<input type="checkbox">문자<a href="#"><img class="leftarrow" src="./images/downarrow_ico_main.png" alt="화살표" style="width:4%"></a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- JOIN BTN-->
            <div class="btn_area" style="margin-top:20px">
                <button type="button" id="btnJoin">
                    <span>가입하기</span>
                </button>
            </div>



        </div>
        <!-- content-->

    </div>
    <!-- wrapper -->
    <script src="signup.js"></script>
</body></html>